<TR><TD>
<FONT SIZE="1" FACE="verdana, arial"><B>Updated:</B> August 13th 2000</FONT><BR><BR>
<FONT SIZE="1" COLOR="#FF0000" FACE="ariel"><B>Unfinished</B></FONT><BR><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="verdana, arial">

Speak with Sarkis Ebonblade, Gragrot and Tynicon DLin for these Shadowknight specific quests...<BR><BR>

<B>Bash:</B> This results in the <A HREF="armor_detail.php3?search=860">Sphinx Eye Amulet</A>. You need an Ebon Tessera, a Sphinx Eye Opal, and a Finely Crafted Amulet.<BR><BR>

<B>Smash:</B> This results in a Djinni's Finger Ring. You need a Copper Disk, a Small Sapphire, and a Silver Ring.<BR><BR>

<B>Slash:</B> This results in a <A HREF="armor_detail.php3?search=864">Pegasus Hide Belt</A>. You need a Diaphanous Globe, a piece of dried leather, and a Finely Woven Cloth Belt.<BR><BR>

<B>Disempowerment:</B> This results in a <A HREF="armor_detail.php3?search=861">Blood Sky Faceplate</A>. You need a Griffon Statuette, a Blood Sky Emerald, and Rusted Pauldrons.<BR><BR>

<B>Envenoming:</B> This results in a <A HREF="armor_detail.php3?search=862">Obtenebrate Mithral Guard</A>. You need a Efreeti War Shield, a Dark Spiroc Feather, and a Shard of Obsidian and supposedly need to prove that your soul is envenomed with hatred.<BR><BR>

<B>Raising of the Dead:</B> This results in <A HREF="armor_detail.php3?search=863">Pearlescent Pauldrons</A>. You need a Large Sky Pearl, a Jar of Honey, a Sphinxian Ring, and Fae Pauldrons.<BR><BR>

<B>Necropotence:</B> This results in The Drinker of Blood. You need an Efreeti War Axe, some Dulcet Nectar, a Bloodstained Hilt, and a Blood Sky Ruby.<BR><BR>

